\fB                        [{public_key:public_key(),\fR
\fB                          [{comment, string()} | {hostnames, [string()]}]}],\fR
\fB                    Decoded_auth_keys ::\fR
\fB                        [{public_key:public_key(),\fR
\fB                          [{comment, string()} | {options, [string()]}]}],\fR
\fB                    Attrs :: {Key :: string(), Value :: string()}.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Decodes an SSH file-binary.

.PP
If \fIType\fR is \fIpublic_key\fR the binary can be either an RFC4716 public key or an OpenSSH public key.

.PP
\fBNOTE: \fRThe implementation of the \fIopenssh_key_v1\fR format is still experimental.



